    public abstract class ProtoPlugin
extends SpinePlugin
    A plugin performing code-generation based on a .proto files.
    Implementation Note:
    This class uses Suppliers instead of direct values because at the time of creation Gradle project is not fully evaluated, and the values are not yet defined.
